                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner, and he said, "Has he got his spoons; did he receive the letter?"</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> What else did he say? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> He said he did it in an unguarded moment.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
